    <section class="hero bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
              I'm Tarak Ram, Co-Founder of 
              <a href="https://www.delemate.com" class="text-blue-500 underline hover:text-blue-700" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DeleMate</a> 
              (A Peer-to-Peer Delivery App) and host of 
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@tarakram.18" class="text-blue-500 underline hover:text-blue-700" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tarak's Show</a>. 
              There, I get to sit down with some of the most fascinating minds and share their stories with the world.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Honestly, I’m just someone who loves diving into books, traveling solo (it’s the best therapy!), and meeting new people who always have the coolest stories to share. 
              Let’s just say, life’s never boring around here!
            </p>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-blue-500"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <img 
              src="/images/tarak_ram.png" 
              alt="Tarak Ram" 
              class="rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>  
